OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FUkrainian refugees in      
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25FWales: Free bus travel and 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5FCadw access                
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Ukrainian refugees will be allowed free
OL,6, bus travel in Wales until the end of   
OL,7, September.                             
OL,9,FThey will also get free access to Cadw 
OL,10,Fsites, in addition to the free rail    
OL,11,Ftravel scheme announced in March.      
OL,13,FThe Welcome Ticket scheme, run by the  
OL,14,FWelsh government, will require users to
OL,15,Fshow proof of refugee status.          
OL,17,FThe scheme is voluntary for bus        
OL,18,Fcompanies, but a "majority" of the     
OL,19,Fservices in Wales are expected to be   
OL,20,Fincluded.                              
